<li id="cite_note-15"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15" title="">^</a></b> The Muscogee Creek Nation in 1993 declared that the Muscogee (Creek) Nation could not find Ward Churchill listed on the Muscogee (Creek) Nation Citizenship Rolls--according to Peggy Powell of the Citizenship Board of the Muscogee (Creek) Nation. <cite style="font-style:normal" class="news" id="CITEREFPowell1993">Powell, Peggy (February 22, 1993). "<a href="http://wardchurchill.blogspot.com/2008/07/creek-nation-document-denying.html" class="external text" title="http://wardchurchill.blogspot.com/2008/07/creek-nation-document-denying.html" rel="nofollow">Letter from Peggy J. Powell, Manager Citizenship Board of the Muscogee (Creek) Nation to Mr. Robert Trepp</a>". <i>Muscogee Creek Document</i> (Citizenship Board Muscogee (Creek) Nation)<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://wardchurchill.blogspot.com/2008/07/creek-nation-document-denying.html" class="external free" title="http://wardchurchill.blogspot.com/2008/07/creek-nation-document-denying.html" rel="nofollow">http://wardchurchill.blogspot.com/2008/07/creek-nation-document-denying.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-07-27</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Letter+from+Peggy+J.+Powell%2C+Manager+Citizenship+Board+of+the+Muscogee+%28Creek%29+Nation+to+Mr.+Robert+Trepp&amp;rft.jtitle=Muscogee+Creek+Document&amp;rft.aulast=Powell&amp;rft.aufirst=Peggy&amp;rft.au=Powell%2C+Peggy&amp;rft.date=February+22%2C+1993&amp;rft.pub=Citizenship+Board+Muscogee+%28Creek%29+Nation&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwardchurchill.blogspot.com%2F2008%2F07%2Fcreek-nation-document-denying.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Ward_Churchill"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
