<li id="cite_note-18"><b><a href="#cite_ref-18" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFJaimes1992">Jaimes, M. Annette (1992). <a href="http://books.google.com/books?as_isbn=0896084248" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?as_isbn=0896084248" rel="nofollow">"Federal Indian Identification Policy: A Usurpation of Indigenous Sovereignty in North America"</a>. in Jaimes, M. Annette (ed.). <i>The State of Native America: Genocide, Colonization and Resistance</i>. Boston: <a href="/wiki/South_End_Press" title="South End Press">South End Press</a>. pp.&#160;123–138. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0896084248" class="internal">ISBN 089608424-8</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.google.com/books?as_isbn=0896084248" class="external free" title="http://books.google.com/books?as_isbn=0896084248" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.com/books?as_isbn=0896084248</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Federal+Indian+Identification+Policy%3A+A+Usurpation+of+Indigenous+Sovereignty+in+North+America&amp;rft.atitle=The+State+of+Native+America%3A+Genocide%2C+Colonization+and+Resistance&amp;rft.aulast=Jaimes&amp;rft.aufirst=M.+Annette&amp;rft.au=Jaimes%2C+M.+Annette&amp;rft.date=1992&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B123%E2%80%93138&amp;rft.place=Boston&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BSouth+End+Press%5D%5D&amp;rft.isbn=089608424-8&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fas_isbn%3D0896084248&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Ward_Churchill"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> Churchill told the University of Colorado investigative committee that he wrote this essay in its entirety.</li>
